00:55:00,473 --> 00:55:02,273
こちら、上に上がってきたんですけれども
I've come up here...

686
00:55:02,273 --> 00:55:04,473
まぁ上でね、何をやるのかと
And as for what I'll be doing up here...

687
00:55:04,473 --> 00:55:07,773
まぁ薄々ちょっと、気づいてるんじゃないかなとは
Well, I think you might have a slight idea...

688
00:55:07,773 --> 00:55:09,273
まぁ、思うんですけれども
...is what I'm thinking.

689
00:55:09,773 --> 00:55:11,173
何か分かるかな？
Do you know what it is?

690
00:55:11,273 --> 00:55:13,673
みんな教えて教えて教えて
Everyone, tell me, tell me, tell me!

691
00:55:13,673 --> 00:55:15,673
みんな何だと思う？
What do you all think it is?

692
00:55:15,673 --> 00:55:18,373
何だと思う？
What do you think?

693
00:55:18,473 --> 00:55:22,673
お、もちろんほら私、お、当たってますね、なんと！
Oh, of course, look at me! Oh, you're right! And—

694
00:55:22,673 --> 00:55:24,173
はい、こちら！
Yes, here it is!

695
00:55:24,173 --> 00:55:25,673
なんとこちらです！
It's actually this!

696
00:55:25,773 --> 00:55:26,673
ドドン！
Ta-da!

697
00:55:26,773 --> 00:55:30,673
新曲『花吹雪』でーす！やったー！
It's my new song, 'Hanafubuki'! Yay!

698
00:55:27,173 --> 00:55:32,173
花吹雪 HANAFUBUKI / 2025.09.04 Release
Hanafubuki / 2025.09.04 Release

699
00:55:32,173 --> 00:55:35,673
いやぁもうだいぶ長らくお待たせしたと思うんですけれども
I think I've kept you waiting for quite a while,

700
00:55:35,673 --> 00:55:38,673
余様のオリジナル曲の新しいのはいつだ？みたいなね
waiting and asking, 'When's the new original song?'

701
00:55:38,673 --> 00:55:41,673
感じで待っていたかと思うんですけれども
I imagine that's how you've been feeling,

702
00:55:41,673 --> 00:55:45,473
えーこちら、えー作詞・作曲Vellさんに書いていただきました
well, this song was written and composed by Vell-san.

703
00:55:45,473 --> 00:55:47,473
ありがとうございます！
Thank you very much!

704
00:55:48,473 --> 00:55:52,673
テーマはですね、可憐な歌声×和風ロック
The theme is 'Lovely Vocals x Japanese-style Rock'.

705
00:55:52,673 --> 00:55:56,673
可愛いだけじゃない、一味違うオリジナルソングとなっております
It's an original song that's more than just cute.

706
00:56:00,173 --> 00:56:03,673
はい、このね、こう綺麗な可憐で重厚な和風ロックとなっておりますので
Yes, it's a beautiful, lovely, yet heavy rock song,

707
00:56:03,673 --> 00:56:07,173
メロディとかね、歌詞もこだわり抜いて磨き上げていただいた楽曲となっておりますので
so the melody and lyrics have been polished with care.

708
00:56:07,173 --> 00:56:10,673
ぜひぜひ皆さん、聴いてください
So everyone, please, please give it a listen.

709
00:56:10,973 --> 00:56:14,173
9月4日0時から、本日の0時からですね
From September 4th at midnight—tonight at midnight—

710
00:56:14,173 --> 00:56:18,173
各種音楽サイトでリリースされるのでぜひ聴いてください
it'll be out on music sites, so please check it out.

711
00:56:18,173 --> 00:56:21,173
聴いてね！いっぱい聴いてね！
Listen to it! Listen to it a lot!

712
00:56:21,673 --> 00:56:24,673
はい、それでは皆さん、大変長らくお待たせいたしました
Alright then, everyone, thank you for waiting.

713
00:56:24,673 --> 00:56:27,673
最後はこの新曲『花吹雪』で送らせていただきたいと思います
I'd like to end with my new song, 'Hanafubuki'.

714
00:56:27,673 --> 00:56:31,173
感想などもね、この衣装もステージと一緒にポストしてください
Please post your thoughts on the outfit and stage.

715
00:56:31,173 --> 00:56:34,173
たくさんポストしてね！
Post a lot, okay!

716
00:56:34,173 --> 00:56:37,173
最後にはですね、メン限パートでちょっと衣装のお写真になったり
Finally, in the members-only part, I'll show photos,

717
00:56:37,173 --> 00:56:40,673
詳しい感じのお話もしたり、ミニライブもありますので
talk more about it, and have a mini-live,

718
00:56:40,673 --> 00:56:44,173
そちらの方もぜひぜひ見に来てくれたら嬉しいです
so I'd be happy if you came to watch that too.

719
00:56:44,673 --> 00:56:46,173
はい、それでは聴いてください
Alright then, please listen.

720
00:56:46,473 --> 00:56:47,673
『花吹雪』
'Hanafubuki'.

721
00:57:11,373 --> 00:57:13,373
共に散る
To scatter together...

722
00:57:13,373 --> 00:57:15,373
宿命なら
if that is our fate,

723
00:57:15,373 --> 00:57:18,673
派手に散りましょう
let's scatter grandly.

724
00:57:18,773 --> 00:57:22,173
花吹雪
Hanafubuki (Storm of Blossoms)

725
00:57:33,073 --> 00:57:35,973
ひらひら舞い落ちる空
Fluttering and dancing down from the sky,

726
00:57:35,973 --> 00:57:39,273
徒に散った泡沫の夢
a transient dream that scattered in vain.

727
00:57:39,373 --> 00:57:42,873
千の華は麗しく咲く
A thousand flowers bloom beautifully,

728
00:57:42,873 --> 00:57:47,773
叶う逢瀬は刹那
the tryst we fulfill is but a moment.

729
00:57:48,473 --> 00:57:51,373
艶やかに舞り
Dancing glamorously,

730
00:57:51,373 --> 00:57:54,373
蝶の儚き命
the ephemeral life of a butterfly.

731
00:57:54,373 --> 00:57:57,573
するり堕ちる今宵は何処
Slipping and falling, where is tonight?

732
00:57:57,573 --> 00:58:00,973
天つ風揺れる
The heavenly wind sways.

733
00:58:03,273 --> 00:58:06,073
狂おしく今咲き誇れ
Bloom proudly now, almost maddeningly.

734
00:58:06,273 --> 00:58:08,273
共に散る
To scatter together...

735
00:58:08,273 --> 00:58:10,273
宿命なら
if that is our fate,

736
00:58:10,273 --> 00:58:13,273
光満ちた舞台ではない
not on a stage filled with light.

737
00:58:13,273 --> 00:58:16,273
闇を裂く旋律は
The melody that tears through the darkness,

738
00:58:16,273 --> 00:58:19,573
ゆらりと香る
fragrant and swaying.

739
00:58:19,573 --> 00:58:21,973
夢を咲かせましょう
Let's make the dream bloom.

740
00:58:22,073 --> 00:58:25,673
花吹雪
Hanafubuki (Storm of Blossoms)

741
00:58:30,273 --> 00:58:33,073
くらくら燃ゆるは焔
Dizzying and burning is the flame,

742
00:58:33,173 --> 00:58:35,973
遠く咲いた明日の夢
a dream of tomorrow blooming far away.

743
00:58:36,173 --> 00:58:39,173
正か否か惑わずに往こう
Let's go without wondering if it's right or wrong,

744
00:58:39,173 --> 00:58:42,473
過去の痛みを胸に
keeping the pain of the past in our hearts.

745
00:58:43,173 --> 00:58:46,073
誰そ彼に
In the twilight,

746
00:58:46,073 --> 00:58:49,073
祈りをひとつ
a single prayer.

747
00:58:49,173 --> 00:58:52,173
涙の川
The river of tears,

748
00:58:52,173 --> 00:58:55,573
穿つ声響く
pierced by the echoing voice.

749
00:58:58,373 --> 00:59:00,973
慎ましくただ進むだけ
Simply moving forward with humility.

750
00:59:01,373 --> 00:59:04,373
茜さす空の果てで
At the edge of the madder-red sky,

751
00:59:04,373 --> 00:59:07,573
褪せた過去の憧れを見る
I see the faded longings of the past.

752
00:59:07,673 --> 00:59:11,073
澄み渡る静寂に
In the clear stillness,

753
00:59:11,073 --> 00:59:14,473
未来を繋ぐ
connecting to the future.

754
00:59:14,673 --> 00:59:18,473
答え求むれど
Searching for an answer,

755
00:59:18,473 --> 00:59:21,173
にべも無し
but finding no sign of one.

756
01:00:01,148 --> 01:00:04,098
共に散る宿命なら
If it is fate to scatter together,

757
01:00:04,548 --> 01:00:07,348
光満ちた舞台で笑え
Smile on the stage filled with light.

758
01:00:07,648 --> 01:00:08,848
闇を裂く
Tearing through the darkness,

759
01:00:09,048 --> 01:00:10,648
旋律は
the melody...

760
01:00:11,048 --> 01:00:14,148
ゆらりと薫る
sways and scents.

761
01:00:14,548 --> 01:00:16,948
夢を咲かせましょう
Let us make our dreams bloom,

762
01:00:17,298 --> 01:00:22,648
花吹雪
a flower blizzard.

763
01:01:53,148 --> 01:01:57,148
7周年ライブ見てくれてありがとう！！
Thank you for watching the 7th anniversary live!!

764
01:01:57,148 --> 01:02:01,148
新衣装にキレイなステージどうだったかな！？
How did you like the new outfit and beautiful stage!?

765
01:02:01,148 --> 01:02:05,148
みんなが少しでも笑顔になってくれたら嬉しいです！！
I'd be happy if it made you smile even just a little!!

766
01:02:05,148 --> 01:02:10,148
8年目もよろしくね～～！！！！！
百鬼あやめ
Please support me in my 8th year too~~!!!!!
- Nakiri Ayame

